This generator produces machine-readable OSCAL artifacts (catalog, 20x and rev5 profile shells, and a
CR26 ↔ NIST SP 800-53 rev5 mapping collection) from FedRAMP Consolidated Rules 2026 Public Preview
data. The repository is explicitly unaffiliated with FedRAMP, GSA, NIST, or the OSCAL project, and its
output is treated by uiao as reference input rather than canon authority. See
src/uiao/canon/compliance/reference/fedramp-cr26/README.md for usage scope and the canon-anchored
companion docs (UIAO_133, ADR-047).

